name: kraken-wallet-cryptoicons
description: Internal Cryptoicons package. Contents mirror that of the remote Cryptoicons package, https://github.com/Cryptofonts/cryptoicons/tree/master/SVG. This is a preliminary step in moving away from Cryptowatch Beacons. In the future, as we move towards a more scalable solution, this could helps us create/integrate a KX-owned remote package.
